  "texts": [
    "Our method outperforms our baselines along with more efficiency.2 Related work 3D Scene UnderstandingThe 3D scene understanding is similar to existing visual question answering.",
    "This concept is termed as \"3D-language scene understanding\" and contains various downstream tasks: 3D Question Answering [13], requires models to answer questions based on 3D scenes; 3D Visual Grounding [9] employs models to localize target objects in 3D scenes according to language queries.",
    "While traditional methods which excel in specific tasks, but these models often lack adaptability to other tasks.",
    "In contrast, 3D Multi-modal Large language models (3D-LLMs) can utilize an unified architecture to perform 3D scene understanding covering 3D VQA and 3D grounding, owing to the reasoning and understanding capabilities inherent in LLMs.",
    "3D Multi-modal Large Language ModelsInspired by remarkable capabilities of LLMs, researchers develop Multi-modal LLMs (MLLMs) by leveraging these models for multi-modal tasks."
  ],
